OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWill a Picasso sold to flee
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthe Nazis be returned?     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In 1938, fearing for their lives amid  
OL,6, rising Jewish persecution, Karl and    
OL,7, Rosi Adler fled Nazi Germany for       
OL,8, then-unoccupied Europe.                
OL,10,FIn order to pay for their short-term   
OL,11,Fvisas, they sold one of their prized   
OL,12,Fpossessions - a 1904 painting by Pablo 
OL,13,FPicasso called Woman Ironing.          
OL,15,FThat painting eventually made its way  
OL,16,Finto the collection of the Solomon R   
OL,17,FGuggenheim Museum in New York City.    
OL,19,FNow, the heirs of the Adlers want the  
OL,20,Fpainting back.                         
